inclusion.criterion: enrolled on the SJLIFE protocol at St. Jude Children's Research Hospital
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: live within a 45-minute drive of a greater Memphis area ATC Fitness Center
inclusion.label: not_met

inclusion.criterion: low lean mass defined as either: Age- and sex-specific relative lean muscle mass standard deviation score ≤ -1.0.
inclusion.label: unknown

inclusion.criterion: Body fat content greater than or equal to 25% in males or greater than or equal to 35% in females
inclusion.label: not_met

exclusion.criterion: Currently pregnant (assessed by serum pregnancy test)
exclusion.label: unknown

exclusion.criterion: Contraindications to resistance training or protein supplementation (e.g. renal) verified by a physician
exclusion.label: not_met

notes: Patient has metastatic papillary thyroid cancer and underwent XRT, which may be a contraindication for resistance training or protein supplementation.
